<hr />
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-cn-1111/Screenshot_2018-12-13-22-56-39.png" style="width:100%;" alt="Screenshot_2018-12-13-22-56-39.png" class="image" />
